This Application is created in Fulfillment of the course IAS2253, Computer and Network Security, Under the Tutelage of Mr. Suhaimi Ramdzan It is develop for the purpose of practicalising Cryptography. By using Vigenere Cipher, the application is able to Encrypt and Decrypt Text Files and Ordinary Texts.
Developed by Mustapha Taiwo, BSc. Computer Science (Software Enginnerng) (Hons.), Department of Software Engineering, Faculty of Computer Science and I.T, University of Selangor (UNISEL).
